OL,3,CFormer colleagues remember Ann
OL,4,CWiddecombe in the town she was MP in
OL,5,Cfor 23 years
OL,7,FAt St Francis Catholic Church in
OL,8,FMaidstone in Kent there were prayers
OL,9,Fthis morning for their former
OL,10,Fparishioner and MP Ann Widdecombe. She
OL,11,Fwas a devout Catholic, known for her
OL,12,Ftraditional values.
OL,14,FAnn Widdecombe was found dead at her
OL,15,Fhome on Thursday. Police have said
OL,16,Fthey believe she was attacked the day
OL,17,Fbefore and a murder investigation is
OL,18,Fongoing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
