OL,3,CFormer colleagues remember Ann
OL,4,CWiddecombe in the town she was MP in
OL,5,Cfor 23 years
OL,7,FShe was MP for Maidstone for 23 years
OL,8,Fand worked as a Home Office and
OL,9,Femployment minister in John Major's
OL,10,Fgovernment between 1994 and 1997.
OL,12,FConservative Helen Grant, who serves
OL,13,Fas the MP for Maidstone and Malling
OL,14,Fand who took over from Miss Widdecombe
OL,15,Ffollowing the 2010 general election,
OL,16,Fhas said she's forever grateful for
OL,17,Fher help.
OL,19,F"(Ann) came to campaign with me at the
OL,20,F2010 election and the 2015 election,"
OL,21,FGrant said.
OL,26,@{D@Bpm{D@Fpn
