OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783950571
OL,3,CFormer colleagues remember Ann
OL,4,CWiddecombe in the town she was MP in
OL,5,Cfor 23 years
OL,7,FGary Cooke, Maidstone Borough
OL,8,FCouncillor and a Conservative Party
OL,9,Fmember, fondly remembered time spent
OL,10,Fwith Miss Widdecombe on the campaign
OL,11,Ftrail.
OL,13,F"(Ann) was forthright, she was
OL,14,Fenergetic," Cooke said. "If she
OL,15,Fthought something was worth doing,
OL,16,Fthen it was worth giving it your all."
